version_description: Complete with intro, full chorus and second verse
Changed incorrect Em chords to G/B (falling bass line), A chords to A7, first F to F/C in verses. Added ending and interludes.
Only other version is inaccurate. I believe this version is more true to the real chords.
Take That single from Feb 17,easily played on acoustic guitar,or if using Classic Electric add Chorus,Reverb effects.

The 7th and slash chord voicings work better with the overall tonality of the song. It seems to me this song was written on acoustic guitar, strumming these simple 2 and 3 finger chords. Once you play it this way, it fits together better than with full open chords.
